2/25/2015: If you don’t reveal a Dragon card from your hand, you must control a Dragon as you are finished casting the spell to get the bonus. For example, if you lose control of your only Dragon while casting the spell (because, for example, you sacrificed it to activate a mana ability), you won’t get the bonus.','W',NULL,'0.02','0.2','0.99',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'W',NULL,NULL,'Orateur d''Ojutaï','Orator des Ojutai','Oratore di Ojutai','オジュタイの語り部','Orador de Ojutai',NULL,'Orador de Ójutai',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Créature : oiseau et moine','Kreatur — Vogel, Mönch','Creatura — Monaco Uccello','クリーチャー ― 鳥・モンク','Criatura — Ave Monge',NULL,'Criatura — Monje ave',NULL,NULL,NULL,'En tant que coût supplémentaire pour lancer l''Orateur d''Ojutaï, vous pouvez révéler une carte de dragon de votre main.£Défenseur, vol£Quand l''Orateur d''Ojutaï arrive sur le champ de bataille, si vous avez révélé une carte de dragon ou si vous contrôliez un dragon au moment où vous avez lancé l''Orateur d''Ojutaï, piochez une carte.','Als zusätzliche Kosten, um den Orator des Ojutai zu wirken, kannst du eine Drache-Karte aus deiner Hand offen vorzeigen.£Verteidiger, Fliegend£Wenn der Orator des Ojutai ins Spiel kommt und falls du eine Drache-Karte vorgezeigt oder einen Drachen kontrolliert hast, sowie du den Orator des Ojutai gewirkt hast, ziehe eine Karte.','Come costo addizionale per lanciare l''Oratore di Ojutai, puoi rivelare una carta Drago dalla tua mano.£Difensore, volare£Quando l''Oratore di Ojutai entra nel campo di battaglia, se hai rivelato una carta Drago o controllavi un Drago mentre hai lanciato l''Oratore di Ojutai, pesca una carta.','オジュタイの語り部を唱えるための追加コストとして、あなたはあなたの手札からドラゴン・カード１枚を公開してもよい。£防衛、飛行£オジュタイの語り部が戦場に出たとき、あなたがオジュタイの語り部を唱えた時点でドラゴン・カードを公開したかドラゴンをコントロールしていた場合、カードを１枚引く。','Como custo adicional para conjurar Orador de Ojutai, você pode revelar um card de Dragão da sua mão.£Defensor, voar£Quando Orador de Ojutai entrar no campo de batalha, se você tiver revelado um card de Dragão ou controlado um Dragão conforme conjurava Orador de Ojutai, compre um card.',NULL,'Como coste adicional para lanzar el Orador de Ójutai, puedes mostrar una carta de Dragón de tu mano.£Defensor, vuela.£Cuando el Orador de Ójutai entre al campo de batalla, si mostraste una carta de Dragón o controlabas un Dragón al lanzar el Orador de Ójutai, roba una carta.',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),('433000','Oreskos Explorer','C17','Creature — Cat Scout','U','{1}{W}','2','2','2',NULL,'When Oreskos Explorer enters the battlefield, search your library for up to X Plains cards, where X is the number of players who control more lands than you. Reveal those cards, put them into your hand, then shuffle your library.',NULL,NULL,'Winona Nelson','68','5','£11/4/2015: The value of X is determined as Oreskos Explorer’s triggered ability resolves.£11/4/2015: If no player controls more lands than you do, you’ll still search and shuffle your library, although you can’t find any cards.','W',NULL,'0.07','0.24','0.99',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'W',NULL,NULL,'Exploratrice d''Oreskos','Oreskos-Erforscherin','Esploratrice di Oreskos','オレスコスの探険者','Exploradora de Oreskos',NULL,'Exploradora de Oreskos',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Créature : chat et éclaireur','Kreatur — Katze, Späher','Creatura — Esploratore Felino','クリーチャー ― 猫・スカウト','Criatura — Felino Batedor',NULL,'Criatura — Explorador felino',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Quand l''Exploratrice d''Oreskos arrive sur le champ de bataille, cherchez dans votre bibliothèque jusqu''à X cartes de plaine, X étant le nombre de joueurs qui contrôlent plus de terrains que vous. Révélez ces cartes, mettez-les dans votre main, puis mélangez votre bibliothèque.','Wenn die Oreskos-Erforscherin ins Spiel kommt, durchsuche deine Bibliothek nach bis zu X Ebene-Karten, wobei X gleich der Anzahl an Spielern ist, die mehr Länder als du kontrollieren. Zeige die Karten offen vor und nimm sie auf deine Hand. Mische danach deine Bibliothek.','Quando l''Esploratrice di Oreskos entra nel campo di battaglia, passa in rassegna il tuo grimorio per trovare fino a X carte Pianura, dove X è il numero di giocatori che controllano più terre di te. Rivela quelle carte e aggiungile alla tua mano, poi rimescola il tuo grimorio.','オレスコスの探険者が戦場に出たとき、あなたのライブラリーから平地・カードを最大Ｘ枚探す。Ｘは土地をあなたより多くコントロールしているプレイヤーの総数に等しい。それらのカードを公開してあなたの手札に加え、その後あなたのライブラリーを切り直す。','Quando Exploradora de Oreskos entrar no campo de batalha, procure em seu grimório até X cards de Planície, sendo X o número de jogadores que controlam mais terrenos que você. Revele aqueles cards, coloque-os em sua mão e, em seguida, embaralhe seu grimório.',NULL,'Cuando la Exploradora de Oreskos entre al campo de batalla, busca en tu biblioteca hasta X cartas de Llanura, donde X es la cantidad de jugadores que controlan más tierras que tú. Muestra esas cartas, ponlas en tu mano y luego baraja tu biblioteca.',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),('433200','Orzhov Basilica','C17','Land','C',NULL,'0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Orzhov Basilica enters the battlefield tapped.£When Orzhov Basilica enters the battlefield, return a land you control to its owner''s hand.£{T}: Add {W}{B}.',NULL,NULL,'John Avon','268','5','£4/15/2013: If this land enters the battlefield and you control no other lands, its ability will force you to return it to your hand.','L','{W}{B}','0.08','0.25','0.99',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'WB',NULL,NULL,'Basilique d''Orzhov','Orzhov-Basilika','Basilica Orzhov','オルゾフの聖堂','Basílica Orzhov',NULL,'Basílica orzhov',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Terrain','Land','Terra','土地','Terreno',NULL,'Tierra',NULL,NULL,NULL,'La Basilique d''Orzhov arrive sur le champ de bataille engagée.£Quand la Basilique d''Orzhov arrive sur le champ de bataille, renvoyez un terrain que vous contrôlez dans la main de son propriétaire.£{T} : Ajoutez {W}{B} à votre réserve.','Die Orzhov-Basilika kommt getappt ins Spiel.£Wenn die Orzhov-Basilika ins Spiel kommt, bringe ein Land, das du kontrollierst, auf die Hand seines Besitzers zurück.£{T}: Erhöhe deinen Manavorrat um {W}{B}.','La Basilica Orzhov entra nel campo di battaglia TAPpata.£Quando la Basilica Orzhov entra nel campo di battaglia, fai tornare una terra che controlli in mano al suo proprietario.£{T}: Aggiungi {W}{B} alla tua riserva di mana.','オルゾフの聖堂はタップ状態で戦場に出る。£オルゾフの聖堂が戦場に出たとき、あなたがコントロールする土地１つをオーナーの手札に戻す。£{T}：あなたのマナ・プールに{W}{B}を加える。','Basílica Orzhov entra no campo de batalha virado.£Quando Basílica Orzhov entrar no campo de batalha, devolva um terreno que você controla para a mão de seu dono.£{T}: Adicione {W}{B} à sua reserva de mana.',NULL,'La Basílica orzhov entra al campo de batalla girada.£Cuando la Basílica orzhov entre al campo de batalla, regresa una tierra que controlas a la mano de su propietario.£{T}: Agrega {W}{B} a tu reserva de maná.',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),('433201','Orzhov Guildgate','C17','Land — Gate','C',NULL,'0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Orzhov Guildgate enters the battlefield tapped.£{T}: Add {W} or {B}.','#_"We do not believe in hiding our wealth in the shadows. This is Orzhov, and this is how we reward greatness."£—Teysa Karlov, Grand Envoy of Orzhov_#',NULL,'John Avon','269','5','£4/15/2013: The subtype Gate has no special rules significance, but other spells and abilities may refer to it.£4/15/2013: Gate is not a basic land type.','L','{W}{B}','0.02','0.17','0.99',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'WB',NULL,NULL,'Porte de la guilde d''Orzhov','Orzhov-Gildeneingang','Cancello della Gilda Orzhov','オルゾフのギルド門','Portão da Guilda Orzhov',NULL,'Portal del Gremio Orzhov',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Terrain : porte','Land — Tor','Terra — Cancello','土地 ― 門','Terreno — Portão',NULL,'Tierra — Portal',NULL,NULL,NULL,'La Porte de la guilde d''Orzhov arrive sur le champ de bataille engagée.£{T} : Ajoutez {W} ou {B} à votre réserve.','Der Orzhov-Gildeneingang kommt getappt ins Spiel.£{T}: Erhöhe deinen Manavorrat um {W} oder {B}.','Il Cancello della Gilda Orzhov entra nel campo di battaglia TAPpato.£{T}: Aggiungi {W} o {B} alla tua riserva di mana.','オルゾフのギルド門はタップ状態で戦場に出る。£{T}：あなたのマナ・プールに{W}か{B}を加える。','Portão da Guilda Orzhov entra no campo de batalha virado.£{T}: Adicione {W} ou {B} à sua reserva de mana.',NULL,'El Portal del Gremio Orzhov entra al campo de batalla girado.£{T}: Agrega {W} o {B} a tu reserva de maná.',NULL,NULL,NULL,'#_« Il nous serait inconcevable de consigner notre richesse à l''obscurité, croyez-le. À Orzhov, c''est ainsi que nous célébrons la grandeur. »£—Teysa Karlov, plénipotentiaire d''Orzhov_#','#_„Wir halten nichts davon, unseren Wohlstand zu verbergen. Wir sind die Orzhov, und so wird bei uns Größe belohnt!"£—Teysa Karlov, Große Gesandte der Orzhov_#','#_"Non pensiamo di dover nascondere le nostre ricchezze nell''ombra. Questi sono gli Orzhov ed è così che premiamo la grandezza."£—Teysa Karlov, Gran Delegata degli Orzhov_#','#_「我らの富を闇に隠そうとは思いません。これがオルゾフで、これが偉大さを賞賛する方法なのです。」£――オルゾフの大特使、テイサ・カルロフ_#','#_"Não acreditamos em esconder nossa riqueza nas sombras. Esta é Orzhov, e para nós é justo recompensar assim a grandeza."£— Teysa Karlov, Grande Enviada dos Orzhov_#',NULL,'#_"No escondemos nuestra riqueza en las sombras. Esto es Orzhov, y así recompensamos la grandeza".£—Teysa Karlov, Gran Enviada de Orzhov_#',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),('433151','Orzhov Signet','C17','Artifact','U','{2}','2',NULL,NULL,NULL,'{1}, {T}: Add {W}{B}.','#_The form of the sigil is just as important as the sigil itself. If it''s carried on a medallion, its bearer is a master. If it''s tattooed on the body, its bearer is a slave._#',NULL,'Martina Pilcerova','219','5',NULL,'A','{W}{B}','0.2','0.35','1.25',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'WB',NULL,NULL,'Cachet d''Orzhov','Orzhov-Petschaft','Sigillo Orzhov','オルゾフの印鑑','Sinete Orzhov',NULL,'Sello orzhov',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Artefact','Artefakt','Artefatto','アーティファクト','Artefato',NULL,'Artefacto',NULL,NULL,NULL,'{1}, {T} : Ajoutez {W}{B} à votre réserve.','{1}, {T}: Erhöhe deinen Manavorrat um {W}{B}.','{1}, {T}: Aggiungi {W}{B} alla tua riserva di mana.','{1}, {T}：あなたのマナ・プールに{W}{B}を加える。','{1}, {T}: Adicione {W}{B} à sua reserva de mana.',NULL,'{1}, {T}: Agrega {W}{B} a tu reserva de maná.',NULL,NULL,NULL,'#_La forme du cachet est aussi importante que le cachet en lui-même. S''il est sur un médaillon, son porteur est un maître. S''il est tatoué, son porteur est un esclave._#','#_Die Form des Siegels ist genauso wichtig wie das Siegel selbst. Wenn es als Anhänger getragen wird, ist sein Träger ein Herr. Wenn es auf den Körper tätowiert ist, ist sein Träger ein Sklave._#','#_La forma del sigillo è importante quanto il sigillo stesso. Se viene portato su un medaglione, chi lo porta è un maestro. Se è tatuato sul corpo, chi lo porta è uno schiavo._#','#_紋章が何にあるかは、紋章自身と同じぐらい重要だ。それが大メダルにあるなら、持ち主は主だ。それが身体の刺青なら、持ち主は奴隷だ。_#','#_A forma do símbolo é tão importante quanto o próprio símbolo. Se é carregado em um medalhão, seu portador é um mestre. Se é tatuado no corpo, seu portador é um escravo._#',NULL,'#_La forma del sello es tan importante como el sello mismo. Si se lleva en un medallón, su portador es un amo. Si está tatuado en el cuerpo, su portador es un esclavo._#',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),('433071','Outpost Siege','C17','Enchantment','R','{3}{R}','4',NULL,NULL,NULL,'As Outpost Siege enters the battlefield, choose Khans or Dragons.£• Khans — At the beginning of your upkeep, exile the top card of your library. Until end of turn, you may play that card.£• Dragons — Whenever a creature you control leaves the battlefield, Outpost Siege deals 1 damage to any target.',NULL,NULL,'Daarken','139','5','£11/24/2014: The card exiled by the “Khans” ability is exiled face up. Playing a card exiled with the “Khans” ability follows the normal rules for playing the card. You must pay its costs, and you must follow all applicable timing rules. For example, if it’s a creature card, you can cast it only during your main phase while the stack is empty.£11/24/2014: If you exile a land card using the “Khans” ability, you may play that land only if you have any available land plays. Normally, this means you can play the land only if you haven’t played a land yet that turn.£11/24/2014: If a noncreature card is manifested and then leaves the battlefield while face down, the “Dragons” ability will trigger.£11/24/2014: Each Siege will have one of the two listed abilities, depending on your choice as it enters the battlefield.£11/24/2014: The words “Khans” and “Dragons” are anchor words, connecting your choice to the appropriate ability. Anchor words are a new rules concept. “[Anchor word] — [Ability]” means “As long as you chose [anchor word] as this permanent entered the battlefield, this permanent has [ability].” Notably, the anchor word “Dragons” has no connection to the creature type Dragon.£11/24/2014: Each of the last two abilities is linked to the first ability. They each refer only to the choice made as a result of the first ability. If a permanent enters the battlefield as a copy of one of the Sieges, its controller will make a new choice for that Siege. Which ability the copy has won’t depend on the choice made for the original permanent.','R',NULL,'0.15','0.45','1.25',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'R',NULL,NULL,'Siège de l''avant-poste','Belagerung des Außenpostens','Assedio dell''Avamposto','前哨地の包囲','Cerco ao Posto Avançado',NULL,'Asedio al destacamento',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Enchantement','Verzauberung','Incantesimo','エンチャント','Encantamento',NULL,'Encantamiento',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Au moment où le Siège de l''avant-poste arrive sur le champ de bataille, choisissez Khans ou Dragons.£• Khans — Au début de votre entretien, exilez la carte du dessus de votre bibliothèque. Jusqu''à la fin du tour, vous pouvez jouer cette carte.£• Dragons — À chaque fois qu''une créature que vous contrôlez quitte le champ de bataille, le Siège de l''avant-poste inflige 1 blessure à une cible, créature ou joueur.','Sowie Belagerung des Außenpostens ins Spiel kommt, wähle Khane oder Drachen.£• Khane — Schicke zu Beginn deines Versorgungssegments die oberste Karte deiner Bibliothek ins Exil. Bis zum Ende des Zuges kannst du die Karte spielen.£• Drachen — Immer wenn eine Kreatur, die du kontrollierst, das Spiel verlässt, fügt Belagerung des Außenpostens einer Kreatur oder einem Spieler deiner Wahl 1 Schadenspunkt zu.','Mentre l''Assedio dell''Avamposto entra nel campo di battaglia, scegli Khan o Draghi.£• Khan — All''inizio del tuo mantenimento, esilia la prima carta del tuo grimorio. Fino alla fine del turno, puoi giocare quella carta.£• Draghi — Ogniqualvolta una creatura che controlli lascia il campo di battaglia, l''Assedio dell''Avamposto infligge 1 danno a una creatura o a un giocatore bersaglio.','前哨地の包囲が戦場に出るに際し、カンか龍かを選ぶ。£• カン ― あなたのアップキープの開始時に、あなたのライブラリーの一番上のカードを追放する。ターン終了時まで、あなたはそのカードをプレイしてもよい。£• 龍 ― あなたがコントロールするクリーチャーが１体戦場を離れるたび、クリーチャー１体かプレイヤー１人を対象とする。前哨地の包囲はそれに１点のダメージを与える。','Conforme Cerco ao Posto Avançado entra no campo de batalha, escolha Khans ou Dragões.£• Khans — No início de sua manutenção, exile o card do topo de seu grimório. Até o final do turno, você poderá jogar aquele card.£• Dragões — Toda vez que uma criatura que você controla deixa o campo de batalha, Cerco ao Posto Avançado causa 1 ponto de dano à criatura ou ao jogador alvo.',NULL,'En cuanto el Asedio al destacamento entre al campo de batalla, elige kans o dragones.£• Kans — Al comienzo de tu mantenimiento, exilia la primera carta de tu biblioteca. Hasta el final del turno, puedes jugar esa carta.£• Dragones — Siempre que una criatura que controlas deje el campo de batalla, el Asedio al destacamento hace 1 punto de daño a la criatura o el jugador objetivo.',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),('433050','Painful Truths','C17','Sorcery','R','{2}{B}','3',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Converge — You draw X cards and you lose X life, where X is the number of colors of mana spent to cast Painful Truths.','#_As the Eldrazi spread, no secret that could give Zendikar''s defenders an advantage was considered too dangerous to seek._#',NULL,'Winona Nelson','118','5','£8/25/2015: The maximum number of colors of mana you can spend to cast a spell is five. Colorless is not a color. Note that the cost of a spell with converge may limit how many colors of mana you can spend.£8/25/2015: Unless a spell or ability allows you to, you can’t choose to pay more mana for a spell with a converge ability just to spend more colors of mana. Likewise, if a spell or ability reduces the amount of mana it costs you to cast a spell with converge, you can’t ignore that cost reduction in order to spend more colors of mana.£8/25/2015: If there are any alternative or additional costs to cast a spell with a converge ability, the mana spent to pay those costs will count. For example, if an effect makes sorcery spells cost {1} more to cast, you could pay {W}{U}{B}{R} to cast Radiant Flames and deal 4 damage to each creature.£8/25/2015: If you cast a spell with converge without spending any mana to cast it (perhaps because an effect allowed you to cast it without paying its mana cost), then the number of colors spent to cast it will be zero.£8/25/2015: If a spell with a converge ability is copied, no mana was spent to cast the copy, so the number of colors of mana spent to cast the spell will be zero. The number of colors spent to cast the original spell is not copied.','B',NULL,'0.14','0.39','1.25',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'B',NULL,NULL,'Vérités douloureuses','Schmerzliche Wahrheit','Verità Dolorose','苦い真理','Verdades Dolorosas',NULL,'Verdades que duelen',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Rituel','Hexerei','Stregoneria','ソーサリー','Feitiço',NULL,'Conjuro',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Convergence — Vous piochez X cartes et vous perdez X points de vie, X étant le nombre de couleurs de mana dépensé pour lancer les Vérités douloureuses.','Konvergenz — Du ziehst X Karten und verlierst X Lebenspunkte, wobei X gleich der Anzahl an unterschiedlichen Farben von Mana ist, das ausgegeben wurde, um Schmerzliche Wahrheit zu wirken.','Convergenza — Pesca X carte e perdi X punti vita, dove X è il numero di colori di mana spesi per lanciare le Verità Dolorose.','収斂 ― あなたはカードをＸ枚引き、Ｘ点のライフを失う。Ｘは苦い真理を唱えるために支払われたマナの色の総数に等しい。','Convergir — Você compra X cards e perde X pontos de vida, sendo X o número de cores de mana gasto para conjurar Verdades Dolorosas.',NULL,'Converger — Robas X cartas y pierdes X vidas, donde X es la cantidad de colores de maná usados para lanzar las Verdades que duelen.',NULL,NULL,NULL,'#_Avec la multiplication des Eldrazi, aucun périple n''était trop dangereux s''il permettait de dénicher un secret pouvant avantager les défenseurs de Zendikar._#','#_Als die Eldrazi sich ausbreiteten, scheuten Zendikars Verteidiger auf der Suche nach Geheimnissen, die ihnen einen Vorteil bringen könnten, keine Gefahren._#','#_Con l''avanzata degli Eldrazi, nessun segreto che potesse offrire un vantaggio ai difensori di Zendikar venne considerato troppo pericoloso da perseguire._#','#_エルドラージが増えるにつれ、ゼンディカー防衛隊を有利にする秘密であれば、探すのに命を惜しむ者は少なくなっていった。_#','#_Conforme os Eldrazi se alastraram, nenhum segredo que pudesse dar alguma vantagem aos defensores de Zendikar foi considerado perigoso demais para ser investigado._#',NULL,'#_A medida que los Eldrazi avanzaban, se dejó de pensar en los riesgos de cualquier secreto que otorgara ventaja a los defensores de Zendikar._#',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),('433051','Palace Siege','C17','Enchantment','R','{3}{B}{B}','5',NULL,NULL,NULL,'As Palace Siege enters the battlefield, choose Khans or Dragons.£• Khans — At the beginning of your upkeep, return target creature card from your graveyard to your hand.£• Dragons — At the beginning of your upkeep, each opponent loses 2 life and you gain 2 life.',NULL,NULL,'Slawomir Maniak','119','5','£11/24/2014: Each Siege will have one of the two listed abilities, depending on your choice as it enters the battlefield.£11/24/2014: The words “Khans” and “Dragons” are anchor words, connecting your choice to the appropriate ability. Anchor words are a new rules concept. “[Anchor word] — [Ability]” means “As long as you chose [anchor word] as this permanent entered the battlefield, this permanent has [ability].” Notably, the anchor word “Dragons” has no connection to the creature type Dragon.£11/24/2014: Each of the last two abilities is linked to the first ability. They each refer only to the choice made as a result of the first ability. If a permanent enters the battlefield as a copy of one of the Sieges, its controller will make a new choice for that Siege. Which ability the copy has won’t depend on the choice made for the original permanent.','B',NULL,'0.27','0.49','1.25',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'B',NULL,NULL,'Siège du palais','Belagerung des Palastes','Assedio del Palazzo','宮殿の包囲','Cerco ao Palácio',NULL,'Asedio al palacio',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Enchantement','Verzauberung','Incantesimo','エンチャント','Encantamento',NULL,'Encantamiento',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Au moment où le Siège du palais arrive sur le champ de bataille, choisissez Khans ou Dragons.£• Khans — Au début de votre entretien, renvoyez une carte de créature ciblée depuis votre cimetière dans votre main.£• Dragons — Au début de votre entretien, chaque adversaire perd 2 points de vie et vous gagnez 2 points de vie.','Sowie Belagerung des Palastes ins Spiel kommt, wähle Khane oder Drachen.£• Khane — Bringe zu Beginn deines Versorgungssegments eine Kreaturenkarte deiner Wahl aus deinem Friedhof auf deine Hand zurück.£• Drachen — Zu Beginn deines Versorgungssegments verliert jeder Gegner 2 Lebenspunkte und du erhältst 2 Lebenspunkte dazu.','Mentre l''Assedio del Palazzo entra nel campo di battaglia, scegli Khan o Draghi.£• Khan — All''inizio del tuo mantenimento, riprendi in mano una carta creatura bersaglio dal tuo cimitero.£• Draghi — All''inizio del tuo mantenimento, ogni avversario perde 2 punti vita e tu guadagni 2 punti vita.','宮殿の包囲が戦場に出るに際し、カンか龍かを選ぶ。£• カン ― あなたのアップキープの開始時に、あなたの墓地からクリーチャー・カード１枚を対象とし、それをあなたの手札に戻す。£• 龍 ― あなたのアップキープの開始時に、各対戦相手はそれぞれ２点のライフを失い、あなたは２点のライフを得る。','Conforme Cerco ao Palácio entra no campo de batalha, escolha Khans ou Dragões.£• Khans — No início de sua manutenção, devolva o card de criatura alvo de seu cemitério para sua mão.£• Dragões — No começo da sua manutenção, cada oponente perde 2 pontos de vida e você ganha 2 pontos de vida.',NULL,'En cuanto el Asedio al palacio entre al campo de batalla, elige kans o dragones.£• Kans — Al comienzo de tu mantenimiento, regresa la carta de criatura objetivo de tu cementerio a tu mano.£• Dragones — Al comienzo de tu mantenimiento, cada oponente pierde 2 vidas y tú ganas 2 vidas.',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),('433297','Path of Ancestry','C17','Land','C',NULL,'0',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Path of Ancestry enters the battlefield tapped.£{T}: Add one mana of any color in your commander''s color identity. When that mana is spent to cast a creature spell that shares a creature type with your commander, scry 1.',NULL,NULL,'Alayna Danner','56','5','£8/25/2017: The color identity of your commander is set before the game begins and doesn’t change during the game, even if your commander is in a hidden zone (like the hand or library) or an effect changes your commander’s color.£8/25/2017: Your commander’s creature types are checked immediately after you cast a creature spell spending mana from Path of Ancestry’s last ability. They aren’t set before the game begins, and they may not be the same types your commander had when you activated that ability.£8/25/2017: If you cast your commander with mana from Path of Ancestry, and your commander hasn’t somehow lost all of its creature types while on the stack, you’ll scry 1.£8/25/2017: If mana from Path of Ancestry is spent to cast a creature spell that shares a type with your commander, you’ll scry 1 before that spell resolves.£8/25/2017: If your commander is in a hidden zone (like the hand or library) or is phased out, it’s considered to have no creature types.£8/25/2017: If your commander has no creature types, it can’t share a creature type with any spell that you cast.£8/25/2017: If Path of Ancestry’s last ability produces two mana (most likely due to Mana Reflection), you’ll scry 1 twice if you spend those two mana to cast one creature spell that shares a type with your commander. You won’t scry 2. You’ll also scry 1 twice if you spend this mana to cast two creature spells that each share a type with your commander.£8/25/2017: On the other hand, if an ability triggers when you tap Path of Ancestry for mana and produces more mana (such as that of Zendikar Resurgent or Mirari’s Wake), you’ll scry 1 only once when you spend those two mana.£8/25/2017: If your commander is a card like Kozilek, Butcher of Truth that has no colors in its color identity, Path of Ancestry’s last ability produces no mana.£8/25/2017: In formats other than Commander, Path of Ancestry’s last ability produces no mana.','L','{W}{U}{B}{R}{G}','3.35','5.36','9.95',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Voie de l''Ascendance','Pfad der Ahnen','Sentiero Ancestrale','祖先の道','Caminho da Ascendência',NULL,'Senda de los ancestros',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Terrain','Land','Terra','土地','Terreno',NULL,'Tierra',NULL,NULL,NULL,'La Voie de l''Ascendance arrive sur le champ de bataille engagée.£{T} : Ajoutez à votre réserve un mana de n''importe quelle couleur de l''identité couleur de votre commandant. Quand ce mana est dépensé pour lancer un sort de créature qui partage un type de créature avec votre commandant, regard 1.','Der Pfad der Ahnen kommt getappt ins Spiel.£{T}: Erhöhe deinen Manavorrat um ein Mana einer beliebigen Farbe der Farbidentität deines Kommandeurs. Wenn dieses Mana verwendet wird, um einen Kreaturenzauber zu wirken, der einen Kreaturentyp mit deinem Kommandeur gemeinsam hat, wende Hellsicht 1 an.','Il Sentiero Ancestrale entra nel campo di battaglia TAPpato.£{T}: Aggiungi alla tua riserva di mana un mana di un qualsiasi colore nell''identità di colore del tuo comandante. Quando quel mana viene speso per lanciare una magia creatura che condivide un tipo di creatura con il tuo comandante, profetizza 1.','祖先の道はタップ状態で戦場に出る。£{T}：あなたのマナ・プールに、あなたの統率者の固有色のうち好きな色１色のマナ１点を加える。このマナがあなたの統率者と共通のクリーチャー・タイプを持つクリーチャー・呪文を唱えるために支払われたとき、占術１を行う。','Caminho da Ascendência entra no campo de batalha virado.£{T}: Adicione a sua reserva de mana um mana de qualquer cor da identidade de cor de seu comandante. Quando aquele mana for gasto para conjurar uma mágica que compartilhe um tipo de criatura com seu comandante, use vidência 1.',NULL,'La Senda de los ancestros entra al campo de batalla girada.£{T}: Agrega a tu reserva de maná un maná de cualquier color en la identidad de color de tu comandante. Cuando ese maná se use para lanzar un hechizo de criatura que comparta un tipo de criatura con tu comandante, adivina 1.',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),('433261','Patron of the Vein','C17','Creature — Vampire Shaman','R','{4}{B}{B}','6','4','4',NULL,'Flying£When Patron of the Vein enters the battlefield, destroy target creature an opponent controls.£Whenever a creature an opponent controls dies, exile it and put a +1/+1 counter on each Vampire you control.',NULL,NULL,'Tommy Arnold','20','5','£8/25/2017: Destroying a creature with Patron of the Vein’s first ability causes its last ability to trigger if Patron of the Vein is still on the battlefield.£8/25/2017: Patron of the Vein’s last ability puts a +1/+1 counter on each Vampire you control, including itself, even if the creature that died can’t be exiled (most likely because it was a